{"article_id":"qKjuiEPFuMPlGeAb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Green New Deal ricocheted into America ' s political consciousness in record time .","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"( D-NY ) ,","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"who drew attention to climate change during a sit-in at House Speaker Nancy Pelosi ' s office","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"before she was even sworn in ,","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"is releasing a formal resolution in the House this week","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"outlining her exact policy proposal for the Green New Deal -","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"an ambitious idea","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"that aggressively tackles climate change","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"to reduce carbon emissions in the next 10 years .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"It also includes plans for universal health care and a significant expansion of the social safety net .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"\" The major thing here is to define it","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"before other people get to define it for her , \"","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"said Waleed Shahid , spokesman for the Justice Democrats .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"\" As multiple 2020 candidates say","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"they support the Green New Deal ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"our movement is going to be defining it","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"to ensure","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that what these candidates are calling for is a World War II-style mobilization of our economy . \"","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Behind the scenes , Ocasio-Cortez and her allies have been mobilizing a campaign","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"to get House Democrats and 2020 presidential candidates to sign onto it","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"- not just in vague platitudes of support ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"but throwing their weight behind the specifics of the deal .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"\" Once this resolution is announced ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"there will be a really clear litmus test for what they support , \"","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"said Stephen O ' Hanlon , spokesman for climate activist group Sunrise Movement .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"But there ' s something larger at work here .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"The Green New Deal is fundamentally about making climate change a central Democratic priority in 2020","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"- without shoving aside health care and the economy .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"After years of this globally important issue languishing on the national agenda ,","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"it has come roaring back .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Until now , the Green New Deal has been more of an idea than an actual policy .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"This week , an Ocasio-Cortez resolution is set to make its debut .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"The plan prioritizes climate change ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"but its strength lies in its symbolic ties to one of the Democratic party ' s biggest historical successes :","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"the original New Deal under President Franklin Delano Roosevelt .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"As historian Eric Rauchway recently wrote in the Washington Post ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"FDR ' s vision for the 1932 New Deal in many ways was a \" green \" New Deal","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"that included a significant social justice component .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"FDR ' s plan included sustainable ways","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"to shape the nation ' s waterways and agriculture ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"trying to ensure","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"there wouldn ' t be another Dust Bowl , the severe drought","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"that came about from poor farming practices .","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"But","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"as Rauchway writes ,","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"FDR ' s social justice idealism fell by the wayside","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"as the president had to compromise","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"to get things done quickly .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"This could be a lesson for politicians","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"who want to make the second version ;","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"the speed and scale","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"required","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"could create problems for marginalized communities .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Activists were clearly inspired by this .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Our original guide for what the Green New Deal looks like","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"lies in a working document","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that called for the formation of a House Select Committee for a Green New Deal","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"( ultimately , House Speaker Nancy Pelosi agreed to a select committee on climate change ,","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"but it did not go as far","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"as progressives hoped ) .","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"The Green New Deal ' s biggest goal is making the United States carbon neutral by 2030","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and turning the country into a global leader in renewable energy in the process .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"This would be a massive transformation ;","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"the document calls for the country to upgrade every residential and industrial building","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"to be energy efficient ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"and completely cut fossil fuel emissions from major industries and US infrastructure .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"The document reads a bit like a progressive manifesto :","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"In addition to calling for the United States to generate 100 percent of its power demand through renewable sources like wind and solar by the year 2030 ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"it also calls for progressive programs like Medicare for all , a jobs guarantee program , and a universal basic income .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"though the actual resolution is expected to focus more on energy and environmental issues ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"the basic structure will likely be similar .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Rather than trying to incentivize private business to change its practices ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"the plan is calling for significant involvement from the federal government for a solution to climate change","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"that ' s both broad enough","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"to meet the scale","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"and fast enough","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"to respond to devastating impacts like sea level rise , drought , fires , and major storms","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"that we are already seeing .","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"\" The level of investment required","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"will be massive , \"","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"the document reads .","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"\" The speed of investment","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"required","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"will be massive .","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"Even if all the billionaires and companies could make the investments","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"required ,","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"they would not be able to pull together a coordinated response in the narrow window of time","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"required to jump-start major new projects and major new sectors . \"","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"As ' s Dave Roberts wrote in his in-depth explainer of the plan :","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"As we will see ,","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"the exact details of the GND remain to be worked out ,","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"but the broad thrust is fairly simple .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"It refers , in the loosest sense , to a massive program of investments in clean-energy jobs and infrastructure ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"meant to transform not just the energy sector , but the entire economy .","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"It is meant both to decarbonize the economy","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"and to make it fairer and more just .","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"If climate change were one of the central policy agenda items among Democrats in this presidential election cycle ,","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"it would be a noticeable departure from the past .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"Democrats have talked about climate change as the most important issue out there for some time ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"but there has been seemingly little urgency in Congress","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"to take action .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"The last large bill","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"House Democrats passed","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"to address climate change","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"was the American Clean Energy and Security Act , a cap-and-trade bill","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"that passed the House in 2009 ;","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"it failed in the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Former President Barack Obama ' s signature climate policy was the Clean Power Plan ;","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"he also joined the international Paris climate agreement .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"President Donald Trump has undone both of those actions ,","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"pulling the US out of the Paris deal","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"and attempting to roll back the Clean Power Plan .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Climate change has been at risk","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"of falling off the agenda permanently -","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"and many conservative groups and leaders","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"( including the current president )","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"love to inject doubt","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"whenever the US is hit with cold temperatures on the well-established fact","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"that climate change is real","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"and caused by humans .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"With Republicans controlling the House and Senate for the first two years of Trump ' s presidency ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"climate change wasn ' t taken seriously on Capitol Hill at all .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"\" We weren ' t even allowed to hold hearings on the issue or things","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"that would contribute to carbon reduction , \"","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"said Rep. Peter DeFazio","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"( D-OR ) ,","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"chairman of the House Transportation and Infrastructure Committee .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"\" The Republicans were a total roadblock","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"for us even talking about climate change .","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"They don ' t believe in it .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Well , some of them do ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"but their leadership and the president certainly don ' t . \"","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"But","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"as ' s Umair Irfan has written ,","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"there are signs","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"that bold ideas","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"to address the crisis","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"are now more welcome .","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"With recent hurricanes , droughts , and raging wildfires","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"all clearly exacerbated by global warming ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"people are experiencing the effects of climate change for themselves ,","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"and more people are getting concerned .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"A recent nationally representative poll from Yale University and George Mason University found","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"69 percent of Americans are \" somewhat worried \" about climate change","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"and 29 percent are \" very worried , \"","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"the highest those numbers have ever been .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"The United States saw billions of dollars in damages and dozens of deaths last year","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"as rising temperatures increased the damages from extreme events .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"These disasters helped make the somewhat abstract warming of the planet tangible in people ' s minds .","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"In other words , the time is now for climate activists and their allies in Congress to make their case for action .","depth":4},{"id":152,"text":"How AOC and activist groups plan to push this policy in the House","depth":3},{"id":153,"text":"The coalition","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"made up of Sunrise Movement , Justice Democrats , and Ocasio-Cortez herself","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"has already gotten about 40 members of Congress to sign onto an effort","depth":6},{"id":157,"text":"pushing for the creation of a select committee on a Green New Deal","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"to hash out the details of the lofty idea .","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"That didn ' t pan out","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"as hoped ;","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"while Pelosi agreed to the creation of a select committee on climate change ,","depth":7},{"id":162,"text":"it wasn ' t as powerful as other committees","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"that have subpoena power","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"- something","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"Ocasio-Cortez and progressive groups wanted .","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"And House leadership has made no commitments yet","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"on actually taking up a Green New Deal resolution","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"when it is released .","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"When the resolution is released ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"activists plan to go back to every House member and senator","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"who supported the select committee","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"and get them to back Ocasio-Cortez ' s updated plan .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"\" For people","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"who have supported the select committee ,","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"we ' re not assuming","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"any of them support the resolution , \"","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"O ' Hanlon said .","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"Even some members","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"who say","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"they support the idea of a Green New Deal","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"say","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"they are wary of signing onto support Ocasio-Cortez ' s resolution","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"without know","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"exactly what the proposal contains .","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"\" I won ' t sign on","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"before I see it , \"","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"DeFazio said .","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"Some 2020 Democrats have also been cautious about a full-throated endorsement .","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"While the Green New Deal has been endorsed by declared or potential candidates","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"including Kamala Harris , Bernie Sanders , Kirsten Gillibrand , Mike Bloomberg , and Cory Booker ,","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"exactly what that means is fuzzy .","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"Staff for 2020 contender Sen. Elizabeth Warren","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"( D-MA )","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"told Axios","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"she supports the \" idea \" of a Green New Deal .","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"The fact","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"this proposal is a catch-all of the most progressive programs","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"means it probably isn ' t going anywhere in the House ,","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"where House Energy and Commerce Chair Frank Pallone has already called the plan too ambitious and unlikely to generate consensus among moderate Democrats in the House , never mind the Senate .","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"\" The goal","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"of trying to reduce fossil fuels","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"and get to a carbon neutral economy","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"is important","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"and something","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"that I agree with , \"","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"Pallone told the Asbury Park Press last month .","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"\" The Green New Deal says","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"you can do it in 10 years .","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"I don ' t know","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"if that ' s technologically feasible .","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"... Beyond that it ' s probably not politically feasible . \"","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"But to Ocasio-Cortez and Green New Deal backers , that ' s not the point .","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"They are banking","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"that the idea will keep spreading .","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"Even some in the House","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"who are skeptical","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"of whether the plan is feasible","depth":11},{"id":218,"text":"agree","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"that the branding of the Green New Deal","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"- harkening back to the days of FDR -","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"is a brilliant marketing strategy .","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"The Green New Deal is becoming a progressive litmus test","depth":3},{"id":223,"text":"Progressives are clearly using the Green New Deal","depth":6},{"id":224,"text":"to push the debate in their direction .","depth":6},{"id":225,"text":"The left wants to make sure","depth":7},{"id":226,"text":"they have fully vetted and influenced the ideas of any Democrats","depth":8},{"id":227,"text":"that have a shot","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"at winning the White House .","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"If Democrats take back the White House and the Senate in 2020","depth":9},{"id":230,"text":"- a big though not impossible if -","depth":9},{"id":231,"text":"activists want to have bills","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"ready to go in 2021","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"to tackle climate change .","depth":9},{"id":234,"text":"Realistically , the bills","depth":9},{"id":235,"text":"that come out of the House in the next two years","depth":9},{"id":236,"text":"probably won ' t be as bold as the proposal","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"Ocasio-Cortez is floating .","depth":9},{"id":238,"text":"Justice Democrats and the Sunrise Movement are clear :","depth":6},{"id":239,"text":"They won ' t support a candidate for president","depth":7},{"id":240,"text":"that won ' t back the Green New Deal .","depth":7},{"id":241,"text":"They ' re aided by the fact","depth":7},{"id":242,"text":"that many 2020 contenders already support Medicare for All ,","depth":8},{"id":243,"text":"and many","depth":10},{"id":244,"text":"- including Booker , Harris , and Sanders -","depth":10},{"id":245,"text":"have already floated some of the other components of a Green New Deal :","depth":10},{"id":246,"text":"a universal basic income and jobs guarantee .","depth":10},{"id":247,"text":"But activists won ' t be totally satisfied","depth":8},{"id":248,"text":"until 2020 candidates do two things :","depth":9},{"id":249,"text":"embrace Ocasio-Cortez ' s plan","depth":10},{"id":250,"text":"and pledge not to take fossil fuel money .","depth":10},{"id":251,"text":"\" We ' re focusing on getting all the 2020 contenders to endorse the full vision of the Green New Deal","depth":10},{"id":252,"text":"and get specific about it , \"","depth":10},{"id":253,"text":"O ' Hanlon said .","depth":9},{"id":254,"text":"\" All of the 2020 candidates need to know","depth":9},{"id":255,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":256,"text":"if they want to be taken seriously by young people ,","depth":11},{"id":257,"text":"they need to reject fossil fuel money and back the Green New Deal . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":515,"left":409,"right":514,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":409,"left":355,"right":408,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":355,"left":283,"right":354,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":276,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":0,"right":275,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":275,"left":267,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":262,"right":266,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":261,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":261,"left":259,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":265,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":6,"right":264,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":7,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":269,"right":273,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":269,"left":268,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":270,"right":272,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":272,"left":16,"right":271,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":282,"left":279,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":19,"right":278,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":20,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":281,"left":280,"right":25,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":354,"left":287,"right":353,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":285,"right":286,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":26,"right":284,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":284,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":353,"left":288,"right":352,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":288,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":352,"left":309,"right":351,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":309,"left":308,"right":54,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":290,"right":307,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":33,"right":289,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":289,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":307,"left":302,"right":306,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":292,"right":301,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":36,"right":291,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":291,"left":37,"right":38,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":296,"right":300,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":296,"left":293,"right":295,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":39,"right":40,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":41,"right":294,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":294,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":298,"right":299,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":298,"left":44,"right":297,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":299,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS